Name:           perl-Time-modules
Version:        2013.0912
Release:        0
Summary:        Various Perl time modules
License:        SUSE-Permissive
Group:          Development/Libraries/Perl
Url:            https://metacpan.org/release/MUIR/Time-modules-2013.0912
